{"tid":940610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【CHINA FREE】據報日本政府疑要求5G營運商通信設備排除中國產品","createTime":"2018-12-14T05:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T06:10:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e320b3b998c8dfb379f01cb8e3da88cc91b72e","tid":940610,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://riceballman.fc2web.com/AA-Illust/Data/ChinaFree.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Friceballman.fc2web.com%2FAA-Illust%2FData%2FChinaFree.png&h=909f3115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1544758246016&amp;issue=20181214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1544758246016%26issue%3D20181214&d=NgsX4dvaM60oeQzAHgI6lBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=df2c2ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1544758246016&amp;issue=20181214</a><br />\n《共同社》報道，日本總務省有意向各手機營運商分配第五代移動通信系統信號頻譜，即5G時的審查標準，要求在基站等部分通信設備中，排除中國產品。有分析認為，日本此舉是針對華為技術和中興通訊的產品，擔心出現訊息外洩等風險。<br />\n<br />\n總務省今日會諮詢電波監理審議會，明年3月計劃向各營運商分配頻譜。相關審查標準草案要求運用5G的公司注意政府的網絡攻擊對策標準，雖然未有直接點名華為及中興，但日本政府早前已決定將兩間機構排除出政府採購清單。而日本三大營運商及新加入的樂天申請分配5G頻譜，都計劃不在通信網絡中使用華為等產品。"},{"pid":"872991367fc09b768b08196c341e45edbc02d937","tid":940610,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bdb1d4212aec64899a88abf25e709bfb6d6e8a","tid":940610,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"又贏"}]}